{"tid":128131,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"去完旅行，想知香港有冇呢份工","createTime":"2017-02-20T14:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T17:39:11.000Z","uid":12482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3259e1cedb82a9a058cd64d99e0c024031c8ec5","tid":128131,"uid":12482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完日本旅行，途中問過幾個係專門服務外地遊客既咨詢人員，眼見佢地識幾種語言又幫到人，真心覺得好勁。<br />\n好想知香港有冇呢啲職位同埋叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dae93981ce904b12475eaa2b955339dd3d216b","tid":128131,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"叫導遊"},{"pid":"fcc2181d8cae4a0e027946a22e487f69aaa24779","tid":128131,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"你識幾多種語言先 ?"},{"pid":"38b8af5ebf2612ef87012b3ac57f3e9660cc0314","tid":128131,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"靠把口去幫人既工 , 喺香港肯定乞食啦 <br />\n<br />\n大把 customer service 都可以幫到人架, 但人工低到爆 <br />\n無香港人會覺得佢地幫到手 or 勁"},{"pid":"8d9b5e1f085944667c8656eb8f523d4b637289d9","tid":128131,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠把口去幫人既工 , 喺香港肯定乞食啦 <br />\n<br />\n大把 customer service 都可以幫到人架, 但人工低到爆 <br />\n無香港人會覺得佢地幫到手 or 勁</blockquote><br />\n識多國語言實無死啦<br />\n香港四大產業係金融,物流,旅遊,工商業<br />\n靠把口去幫人既工要乞食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乞食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82e70670620a42301a22817bf844b392e6cbd8c","tid":128131,"uid":12482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠把口去幫人既工 , 喺香港肯定乞食啦 <br />\n<br />\n大把 customer service 都可以幫到人架, 但人工低到爆 <br />\n無香港人會覺得佢地幫到手 or 勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都有考慮到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我想知有冇啲係專門比外地遊客去咨詢既 而唔係普通既customer service 因為我見好多去呢啲counter 咨詢既反而係香港人大陸人<br />\n定係因為香港太細 唔似其他國家 所以都無咩發展可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5c96eaf84b015ff09c1fd3cba497c8d43fe37c02","tid":128131,"uid":12482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靠把口去幫人既工 , 喺香港肯定乞食啦 <br />\n<br />\n大把 customer service 都可以幫到人架, 但人工低到爆 <br />\n無香港人會覺得佢地幫到手 or 勁</blockquote><br />\n識多國語言實無死啦<br />\n香港四大產業係金融,物流,旅遊,工商業<br />\n靠把口去幫人既工要乞食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乞食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為自己一直搵唔到想做既野 宜家難得搵到一個範疇係自己有興趣 想了解多啲 睇下有冇機會成為一個職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但始終都係要睇錢 如果呢啲職位真係好似巴打咁講會乞食 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb83d27173c42038fd11370abe42ae3a6743272","tid":128131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"旅發局<br />\n<a href=\"http://partnernet.hktb.com/tc/about_hktb/job_opportunities/index.html?id=463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpartnernet.hktb.com%2Ftc%2Fabout_hktb%2Fjob_opportunities%2Findex.html%3Fid%3D463&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=23c01d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://partnernet.hktb.com/tc/about_hktb/job_opportunities/index.html?id=463</a>"},{"pid":"cb1d9d0099318b0ce0be9b4e44cfcd4851746af2","tid":128131,"uid":9823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"香港搵唔到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}